Dating in Canada: meet local singles near you

   EliteSingles has vibrant, intelligent members across Canada looking for
   long-term love. We aim to help them find that love by making meaningful
   introductions that can lead to longer-term commitment. Join
   EliteSingles today for a secure, supportive service and find local
   singles in your city.

Introducing EliteSingles Canada

   Canada is a country of astonishing beauty, wonderful diversity, and
   welcoming charm. From mountains, forests, and prairies to cities,
   seacoasts, and islands, this is a country to suit every taste. What's
   more, Canadians themselves have a globally-renowned reputation for
   conviviality. It may be surprising, however, to hear just how many of
   these warm, vibrant Canadians are single – more than 12 million
   identified as such in the most recent census^1. But there is hope; many
   of these singles are turning to premium Canadian dating sites such as
   EliteSingles to help meet someone who gets them.

A secure and supportive service

   With our dating service, security is a priority. Our dedicated Customer
   Care team is there to help make your Canada dating experience a
   positive one. As well as verifying all profiles to check that our
   members are genuine, we are committed to protecting your data. We use
   SSL Encryption and a Fraud Detection System to ensure the online safety
   of our members.
