Personalized matches for busy Canadians

   Our members are busy professionals who don’t always have the time to
   wade through a sea of online profiles. This is why we do the work for
   you. When you join with us you will receive a selection of local
   suggestions that we believe are compatible with your lifestyle and
   values – a selection we pick using a smart-profiling service that takes
   into account your personality and partner preferences. All you need do
   after completing your profile is get excited about who you might meet!

A matchmaking service to help you meet local singles

   At EliteSingles, we prioritze compatibilty. We understand that a big
   part of this involves location (after all, finding love should enrich,
   not disrupt, your home life). This is why we take your ideal location
   into account before making our tailored profile suggestions. We have
   members hailing from across Canada, making it easier for us to
   recommend like-minded, local singles close to you. What’s more, when
   you join us, we offer a choice of an English or a French speaking
   service, in order to ensure we are creating truly meaningful
   connections in the language of your choice.

   You'd be surprised at just how many compatible singles are nearby. So
   if you are serious about your search for a partner, join the thousands
   of Canadian men and women who are actively looking for that special
   someone. It's time to meet amazing local singles - and you can get
   started right here.

   Get started with EliteSingles!

